High Performance RISC-V Leadership

Our global team is delivering a family of no-compromise, high-performance RISC-V data center-class CPUs with extensible instruction set capability delivered in the form of multi-core chiplets or core IP for high-performance applications in the cloud, enterprise data center, hyperscale, 5G, edge compute, AI/ML and automotive markets.

Technology at Ventana

Highest Performance RISC-V CPU

Performance competitive with the latest Arm and x86 data center CPUs. Easily portable across process nodes.

Chiplets Available for Rapid Productization

Drastic reduction in costs and time to market for custom system designs using leading edge chiplet technology.

Domain Specific Acceleration

Customer innovation through bespoke workload acceleration.

Open Ecosystem

Open standards based RISC-V architecture and chiplet interfaces. Large ecosystem of Strategic IP and SoC chiplet providers to provide turnkey solutions.

Applications

Our technology addresses some of the biggest challenges in industries such as data center, automotive, 5G, AI, and client computing by enabling the quick and efficient creation of RISC-V platforms optimized for their most demanding applications.

View products

Technology

The Ventana Veyron series is the industry’s highest performance RISC-V processors, and is supported by all the necessary system IP needed to create advanced, customized computing platforms.

Ventana Veyron processors are available as chiplets, turnkey platforms, or IP.

Get in touch

Our team would love to hear from you. We are always available to answer any questions you should have.

Ventana Micro Systems Inc. was founded in 2018 to revolutionize the processor market by offering high-performance, extensible and secure compute chiplets based on RISC-V’s open architecture. Ventana is a Premier Member of RISC-V International and part of its Technical Steering Committee.
